{"tid":1404783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好撚自豪我係香港人","createTime":"2019-08-04T06:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T07:32:52.000Z","uid":24807,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc32fdf3a5f2b2ebbd71f63d71d9a1fa1521f34","tid":1404783,"uid":24807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"呢兩個月入面 香港人完美展示左<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">團結 勇敢 有智慧</span></span>呢三樣特質<br />\n無論啲狗係邊區發癲 都會有好多人出黎幫手<br />\n由係地鐵怕手足冇錢買飛而買定一大堆擺度 到食住催淚彈都要提樓上閂窗 定係立法會既要走一齊走<br />\n呢啲畫面一世都唔會唔記得<br />\n以前一直好撚葡萄日本人點解人地個民族性咁撚強 但原來最好既野自己一早已經擁有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真比我投多幾多次胎 我都會做香港人<br />\n如果大家都咁愛香港 唔好放棄 黎明前既黑暗真係好撚黑暗 但我地一定捱得過<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"f9a0eec34e824350172d7bfffeb3a15f168a971d","tid":1404783,"uid":68033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"香港人團結。<br />\n光復香港，<br />\n時代革命。"},{"pid":"466419cfd3150b38381c897d4097315661671577","tid":1404783,"uid":274792,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"認同 有好強既民主意識<br />\n又勇敢、又善良"},{"pid":"45aec652597a756a5dee31b78546f392d7d8a544","tid":1404783,"uid":261470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:09:41.000Z","msg":"得閒係要打個j平衡下<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5a05f00fa8060242bc9f49400bf0532e2fc10d","tid":1404783,"uid":24807,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"以前一路覺得香港人好撚自私 全部都係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到依家咁好似係平行時空過黎咁"},{"pid":"f93417f673b34954d2a659d759e0720482c3a85f","tid":1404783,"uid":40286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候轉下玩法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同狗打 對政府冇影響 <br />\n對真係揸權嘅土共更加冇影響<br />\n要一針見血 就要搵政權最著緊嘅野同佢玩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">錢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[不合作運動全面升級] 不論和理非/勇武，入一入嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3e79786285138947533daf514020c7e2e9282017","tid":1404783,"uid":64003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"一時又話唔比影相 一時又上嚟求相 你玩曬啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1404604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1404604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"26a3a61539e3959907347d9b5cbe48baa7ea0f30","tid":1404783,"uid":191312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"直頭可以同猶太人並駕齊驅"},{"pid":"12c5bf9ee6d24eb5d6a8ef9bac75d68334e8f68d","tid":1404783,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec014b8fdf2c1c6514319fdcedad9344e05060d","tid":1404783,"uid":24807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f93417f673b34954d2a659d759e0720482c3a85f","tid":1404783,"uid":40286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候轉下玩法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同狗打 對政府冇影響 <br />\n對真係揸權嘅土共更加冇影響<br />\n要一針見血 就要搵政權最著緊嘅野同佢玩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">錢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[不合作運動全面升級] 不論和理非/勇武，入一入嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:11:18.000Z","msg":"推 一直覺得不合作運動先係最有用"},{"pid":"0ed226cce52bd2f9ed029237ce58ccbaa57ebb26","tid":1404783,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"